headline: 3 Profitable Stocks with Mounting Challenges
summary: While profitability is essential, it doesn’t guarantee long-term success. Some companies that rest on their margins will lose ground as competition intensifies - as Jeff Bezos said, "Your margin is my opportunity".

headline: COLM Set to Release Q1 Earnings: Key Insights for Investors
summary: Despite a tough U.S. market, Columbia Sportswear's first-quarter performance may have benefited from international growth, product innovation and cost-efficiency efforts.
